itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest actor Neil Brown Jr. who plays Ray on CBS’s “Seal Team” to discuss what it has been like to be an actor during the Coronavirus shutdown, Neil explains why Tekashi 6ix9ine is a real life Joker, he shows us how he works in some of his own personality into the characters he plays, and ends the show by talking about the filming of the hit TV show “Insecure”.
